trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming i en visuelle utformeren for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.TreeViewDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.TreeViewDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the designer action list collection for this designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter designer handlingen liste-samlingen for utformeren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"></xref> associated with this designer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"> </xref> tilknyttet utformeren.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of predefined automatic formatting schemes to display in the **Auto Format** dialog box for the associated control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Henter samling av forhåndsdefinerte automatisk formatering skjemaene skal vises i den **automatisk Format** dialogboksen for den tilknyttede kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"></xref> object that contains the predefined schemes for the control.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"> </xref> objekt som inneholder de forhåndsdefinerte skjemaene for kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Displays a dialog box to edit the line images for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Viser en dialogboks for å redigere bildene linje for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Binds the associated control to the design-time data source.
trans-unit.target: Tilknyttede kontrollen bindes til datakilden utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The data bound control.
trans-unit.target: Dataene som er bundet kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Displays a dialog box to edit the data bindings.
trans-unit.target: Viser en dialogboks for å redigere databindinger i.

trans-unit.source: Displays a dialog box to edit the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeNodeCollection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Viser en dialogboks for redigering av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeNodeCollection"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the HTML markup that is used to represent the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Henter HTML-koden som brukes til å representere kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The markup used to render the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Markup som brukes til å gjengi kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the HTML markup text that is used to render a placeholder for the associated control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Henter HTML markeringsteksten som brukes til å gjengi en plassholder for den tilknyttede kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The markup used to render the control at design time with an empty data source.
trans-unit.target: Markup som brukes til å gjengi kontrollen under utformingen med en tom datakilde.

trans-unit.source: Provides the markup that is used to render the control at design time when an error has occurred.
trans-unit.target: Gir markup som brukes til å gjengi kontrollen under utformingen når det har oppstått en feil.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Exception> that was thrown.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Exception>som oppstod.</xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: The markup used to render the control at design time when an error has occurred.
trans-unit.target: Markup som brukes til å gjengi kontrollen under utformingen når det har oppstått en feil.

trans-unit.source: Constructs a sample data source that can be used at design time for the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Bygger en datakilde i eksemplet som kan brukes på utformingstidspunktet for den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: An object implementing the <xref href="System.Web.UI.IHierarchicalEnumerable"></xref> interface that can be used as a data source for controls derived from <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HierarchicalDataBoundControl"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som implementerer den <xref href="System.Web.UI.IHierarchicalEnumerable"> </xref> grensesnitt som kan brukes som en datakilde for kontroller avledet fra <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HierarchicalDataBoundControl"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, provides for custom initialization of the given <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, gir for egendefinert initialisering av den angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"></xref> that can be cast as a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"> </xref> som kan brukes som en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the control designer uses a temporary preview control to generate the design-time HTML markup.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om kontrollen designer bruker en midlertidig preview-kontroll for å generere utformingen HTML-koden.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>, if the control designer uses a temporary copy of the control for design-time preview; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>, if the control designer uses the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Component*> property for the control contained in the control designer.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>, hvis kontrollen designer bruker en midlertidig kopi av kontrollen for utforming forhåndsvisning; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>, hvis kontrollen designer bruker den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Component*>egenskap for kontrollen i kontrollen utformeren.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Component*>
